data.description: Stately 4 bedroom, 2 full and 2 half bath Colonial situated on over 2 parklike acres with CITY SEWER! This Chardon Colonial has been well taken care of!  Upon driving up, you will notice how majestically the home sets on the property. The spacious entry greets you and showcases the curved staircase.  There is a large formal living room perfect for entertaining. The formal dining room has had a complete makeover including new barn door entry. There is a large eat-in kitchen with loads of cabinetry and breakfast area. There is a first floor laundry and half bath conveniently located off entry to pool area. The rustic family room has a built in bar and brick fireplace that overlooks the parklike backyard. There is also a first floor office.  The second floor owners suite has a spacious bedroom, private bath with jetted tub, and dressing room with center island.  There are 3 additional bedrooms, all nicely sized and full bath. The lower level is partially finished with brick fireplace, perfect for watching movies on a cold evening. Last, but not least is the 20x24 in-ground heated pool that includes a robotic cleaner, solar and winter cover and all equipment. There is also a gazebo and deck for outdoor entertaining. Make your apt today to view this amazing home.
